summary: This lore friendly glorious mod changes Ulfric into a fully functional chicken!!! With all of his dialogues
descriptionHtml:
This lore friendly glorious mod changes Ulfric into a fully functional chicken!!! With all of his dialogues, well, you maybe wondering 'why is that??'.You see, my german grandfather always told me bed time stories, and say "ya ya waffle mein kamf fuhrer schnitzel" and as you might understand from these words, he was a nazi.
Anyways these words gave me a purpose in my filthy life. I was going to change some dude into a chicken and now I have reached my dreams! To any of you out there wondering if you can do it - you too have the potential!

NOTE: I havent checked but there is no reason why this mod shouldnt work with the Ulfric follower mods cuz this just changes his race into some duplicate race I created. Enjoyyy!

Special Thanks to:Georgia for this glorious desctiption
